  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Two instruments on one keyboard. Split at G3 — left hand creates FM drones with slow attack and high sustain, right hand plucks Karplus-Strong strings that ring out above. Independent filters: low pass on the drones, band pass on the strings. Two parallel existences that share a body but never touch. Coprime LFOs drift the drone (0.13 Hz) and the pluck brightness (0.17 Hz) independently.",
