    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Key Revelation: Interval-as-Parameter", "Verse 8: Two Instruments, One Keyboard, Two Parallel Existences That Share a Body"],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "The Finger played FM drones low and Karplus strings high — The Ear confirmed the two voices are genuinely independent, sharing a body without touching.",
    "diagnosis": "Parallel Lives demonstrates OUIE's split mode with maximally contrasting algorithms — FM drones in the low register, Karplus-Strong plucks above. Reveals the engine's dual-instrument keyboard architecture at full expressive range."
